website_summaries.verdict: A traditional entryway console table at a great price.
pros: This lovely table works great as a foyer piece, and its curved cabinets close magnetically for a nice touch
An elegant table that doesn't break the bank
Measures 38 inches wide by 14.5 inches deep by 31.63 inches high
cons: Some customers received tables with cracks or unfinished areas

customer_reviews.title: Great Table for the Price
customer_reviews.text: Easy to put together, arrived in perfect shape. It's smaller than I imagined and it's certainly not going to make a bold statement in a big space. But it works very well as an accent piece in an entryway or back door area and is really quite lovely when properly decorated. As other reviewers indicated, the color is definitely darker than the stock photos, but that is actually part of the reason I ordered it. It matches the dark wood furniture in the rest of the room very well.
customer_reviews.author: Melissa Ortiz

customer_reviews.title: Darker in color than anticipated.
customer_reviews.text: The style and size is exactly what I wanted. If the color had been closer to the photo provided by the seller I would be a happy customer. I won't return it but I also can't use it where I intended to. The lighting is not sufficient there and it looks even darker than this photo which was taken with a flash. Quality is good enough and product arrived undamaged.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon customer

customer_reviews.title: Damaged, had to return
customer_reviews.text: I'm sure this would have looked great in my house, but after carefully unpacking it the whole back corner was smashed in. So, a half hour and tons of tape later, it was back to UPS. Bought one from the competition, and it was fine. This was the second piece of fairly pricey furniture I've bought from Amazon, the first being a large bookcase that came in with a large hole driven completely through the box by a forklift tine judging by the shape. That thing was well over a hundred pounds, and oh so fun to repackage. Never again...
customer_reviews.author: R. Seehoffer

customer_reviews.title: loving this purchase
customer_reviews.text: like a treasured heirloom this piece is by far the most exceptinal purchased i have made in my 53 years of decorating and updating my home. the reason for 5 stars first, the time was less than a wk. the packing was amazing and the conole was well built and finished for the small amt. of money paid 169.00 with free shipping too i placed a crystal lamp ,also purchased from amazon to the riht ide of the console and a fluted round crystal vase with i lg. hydrangea and a sm. peony. on the bottom shelf i put 3 graduated mercury candlesticks. together the ensemble looks like ethan allan store decor
customer_reviews.author: paula stearns

customer_reviews.title: Far exceeds expectations
customer_reviews.text: I have actually never written a review but I absolutely must ~ because this gorgeous new addition to my home is well worth the mention. It is perfect. I read numerous reviews before I decided to make this purchase and sooo pleased in doing sooo. As mentioned by others the color is deeper than appears however the shade is quite stunning. Many people mentioned a slight flaw in the wood on the back corner this must have been noted and corrected mine is flawless the cabinet far exceeded my expectations the detail is so beautiful. I am not handy at all and this piece is so easy to put together. I am exceptionally pleased with my purchase.
customer_reviews.author: Linda

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful and easy to assemble!
customer_reviews.text: This table is absolutely gorgeous and looks way more expensive than it actually is. It is extremely simple to assemble, and feels sturdy without being heavy! We have it in our entryway, and it is both beautiful and functional, as the storage space in the cabinet is surprisingly ample. I will say that it is a bit short (only reaches the chair rail of our wainscoting), but that was easily remedied by adding a tall lamp for visual height and balance.
customer_reviews.author: Brenis Family

customer_reviews.title: Elegant
customer_reviews.text: Very elegant. A bit darker than shown in the picture. Serves my purpose. Assembly was a breeze. 5 stars.
customer_reviews.author: Rajesh Krishnamachari

customer_reviews.title: Saves space, look expensive
customer_reviews.text: This small console table exceeded my expectations! It is darker than shown in the picture and in reality looks much more expensive. It saves space and still can keep lots of things. You cannot find the better table for hallway in your home. Packed well, shipped fast as was promised. Very happy with this purchase!
customer_reviews.author: Lucy

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful Console
customer_reviews.text: I love this product in the my foyer area of my home. The console isn't as long as I would have liked it to be, but the details on the product for the price is worth the cost. It's sturdy and the 2 doors provide excellent storage for small items. The console was easy to assemble, I practically did it by myself. But, after screwing/twisting on the legs to sit the item in an upright position, I had the assistance of my adult son. The color is beautiful/rich and I receive compliments all the time on this piece. I recommend this product if you need a medium/small console for your home.
customer_reviews.author: Carmensita

customer_reviews.title: A little too fragile for our needs, but very pretty and a bargain
customer_reviews.text: The picture looks nice. It was cheaper through Amazon than on the other sites. We had intended to use it in the hall to hold shoes. However, we decided that our family would trash something this fragile. So we got something more casual and sturdier. I never even took this out of the box, so I can't speak to ease of assembly. It is pretty, though, and if you don't intend it for hard use it looks a lot more expensive than it was.
customer_reviews.author: Julie

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful. Sturdy. Well made. Extremely well packed.
customer_reviews.text: I rarely write reviews, but when a reseller does such a great job, I fell compelled to share our experience. Extremely well packed, double boxed with much styrofoam to protect the wood. Minimal assembly required, less than 10 minutes to unpack and assemble and no tools needed. We are using this piece in our entry way under a large, beautiful framed picture. We will definitely buy from this reseller again.
customer_reviews.author: Cary Sholer

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful & Great Quality
customer_reviews.text: Bought this table to put in our open area on the second floor. This is surprisingly good quality, sturdy, and functional. The small doors aren’t just for show, you can open them up and store things inside if you’d like. The wood is a rich brown, and didn’t arrive scratched or damaged. Putting it together was easy and clear, and the product by no means is shoddy workmanship. All in all, this looks way more expensive than what I paid for!
customer_reviews.author: Plunderbunny

customer_reviews.title: Don't Buy👎
customer_reviews.text: Tiny and expensive. It was much trouble to send back so I'm stuck with it and out of 200.00. The storage is descent. I store candals in mine. "not many ". Bottom and top outer shelves are narrow. You can put little decor. I'm disappointed it was a waist😒👎
customer_reviews.author: Katrina

customer_reviews.title: Patience was its own reward
customer_reviews.text: This table takes patience to acquire. It took us two deliveries before we had one that we wanted to keep. Luckily, my husband had read other reviews and knew what to expect. The first one came damaged, but the second one's packaging came with additional support. It made all the difference. Amazon immediately processed our return and replacement. We arranged for UPS to come and pick this item up at our house due to its size. The table itself is very pretty and is a wonderful addition to our foyer. I love looking at it. It's slight semi-circle shape is beautiful. The wood's finish is a nice dark brown. I'm glad that we could be patient and get this table.
customer_reviews.author: Karen K.

customer_reviews.title: Very pleased  with this table!!!!!
customer_reviews.text: This table is everything I want and more. I always look at the reviews and go straight to the bad ones....They really didn't discourage me from purchasing this table. It arrived in a reason amount of time. The packaging was nice and tight. Properly wrapped to endure any mishandling.I was able to assemble it myself. Very nice elegant table. A must buy item.
customer_reviews.author: Kisha

customer_reviews.title: Arrived on time in extremely good condition. I spent about 15 minutes unpacking it
customer_reviews.text: Arrived on time in extremely good condition. I spent about 15 minutes unpacking it, looking it over for damage and putting it together. I only had to attach the 4 upper legs, the bottom shelf then the four lower legs. I have it in the foyer/entryway of my home along with a solid cherry grandfather clock and a Mahogany chest of drawers. The color is right in the middle of the two other pieces. Visitors to my home are commenting positively on it's quality, fit and finish.
customer_reviews.author: THGDriver

customer_reviews.title: Might Think Twice If You Plan to Treat this as Furniture
customer_reviews.text: I have mixed feeling on this one: Pros: The price point is very competitive and the console looks very nice. It arrived on time without any damage and looks like the picture. Had no problem with assembly. Cons: I am not sure how well this item will stand up over time. We just got the piece and unlike most "decorative" items in a home--this one will have to weather some wear and tear (you will put items on it). I am second guessing whether I should have paid a little more a bought a piece of furniture as opposed to what is better described as an ornamental filler.
customer_reviews.author: Lawboss

customer_reviews.title: Entrance Table
customer_reviews.text: I have had this accent table by my entrance for 5 years and still in good shape/condition. I put my keys on it and hide other accessories inside the cabinets. There is a lot of room inside. Design looks appealing too.
customer_reviews.author: Julianne L Wood

customer_reviews.title: Highly recommend.
customer_reviews.text: Perfect piece for the intended location. Easy to assemble. The cabinet is fully assembled. There the 4 legs that screw into the cabinet. Then there is the bottom shelf where the 4 lower legs screw through the shelf and into the upper legs. That's it. I have had pieces that required me to install the door hinges, etc. Not this piece. One note: the lower legs come packaged/attached to the longer legs. Unscrew them and you have all the pieces.
customer_reviews.author: Deb

customer_reviews.title: Looks beautiful and was easy to assemble.
customer_reviews.text: My only complaint is that there are 2 small chips on the right side; paint chipped off. I can fix it with scratch cover but it shouldn't have happened. It was packed very well in thick styrofoam so it had to happen at the factory. After examing the chips, it's apparent that it isn't real wood. However, it is lovely and looks like a quality piece.
customer_reviews.author: Glenda Bolyn

customer_reviews.title: very good but pin to wall for sure!
customer_reviews.text: This is a very good looking foyer table. Good space on top for decoration. Sturdy enough but not really heavy. Has some storage as well and could fit a small single ottoman under for changing shoes etc., assembly is very quick one. It transformed our foyer for sure. The only reason I gave 4 is, it could tip forward and fall if you have kids that try to pull or stand on the front edge. We felt this furniture is more vulnerable than other tables, so we fixed it to the wall with an existing anchor we had, it should have been included with instructions for sure for safety.
customer_reviews.author: Mei

customer_reviews.title: Great accent piece
customer_reviews.text: I love this table but knocking off a star since it’s much darker than the photo. Excellent quality and so easy to assemble. I’m actually using it in my bedroom as a vanity table. Plenty of room to store all the makeup and hair stuff I have out of sight. I left the bottom shelf off and my stool fits exactly underneath it. Mine was packaged very well with a box within a box and everything protected well inside. No quality issues at all
customer_reviews.author: jessica

customer_reviews.title: This is a wonderful piece of furniture for a very affordable price
customer_reviews.text: We were skeptical buying this since it was made in China. However, due to the strength of the reviews, we did purchase. This is a wonderful piece of furniture for a very affordable price! We put it in our entry hall and it looks wonderful. Quality was surprising and the wood is of a medium dark color. Not quite cherry, but close. The item still smelled of varnish. Easy assembly, perhaps 15 minutes to screw in the legs firmly. Nice addition to our decor and certainly doesn't look as cheap as it was. Arrived sturdily packaged and in excellent condition. Just wish we could have found a comparable item made in the US.
customer_reviews.author: Courtney

customer_reviews.title: Poor QA
customer_reviews.text: First one was damaged in shipping, not completely the manufacturer's fault but the foam's impact resistance seems questionable. The second one had a major split at the top of one leg and minor splits at the bottom of three legs. All the splits had paint in them, so it should have been caught. Especially since there was repaired damage in the storage area. We previously purchased two end tables from the manufacturer that work great. But this table we had no luck with. We decided to return for refund instead of another exchange as it is a little shorter than we were wanting for that location anyway.
customer_reviews.author: C. Howard

customer_reviews.title: Adds a Touch of Class
customer_reviews.text: This table is beautiful! It's a little darker than what the picture shows. Other than that, it's exactly what I was looking for. According to other reviews, cracks in the legs are a common problem. Closely inspected mine and didn't find any. In fact, I didn't find any blemishes or damage. I've had it about a week. It's fairly sturdy but I don't think it would stand up to heavy usage for long. I did knock off the inside door magnets when I was putting something inside. Easy fix. Was quick and simple to assemble; takes maybe 10-15 minutes. Looks like a much more expensive piece of furniture and adds a little touch of class to the room.
customer_reviews.author: HazyMeerkat

customer_reviews.title: True Color Not Well Represented!
customer_reviews.text: Item is MUCH darker than as shown, even the reviews didn't prepare me for how dark. I kept it only because it was perfect size for the space, had needed storage and seemed to be well made for the price, but really don't like the stain and finish is a little rough in places. I'm using with a family heirloom, antique wall mirror and Waterford crystal lamp. It provides end table use for a sofa as well as a side table for a chair.
customer_reviews.author: POLLY CARTER

customer_reviews.title: Nice entryway table...
customer_reviews.text: This is a very nice entryway table. We have a nook in the entry way and this tables fits there perfectly. We have a couple of decor items on it and the storage is very handy to keep scented candles,air fresheners and some small items. It has good finish and looks of high quality. Its not real heavy but is good and sturdy. The box had a dent and hole in it but the table was intact. It took me about 15 minutes to assemble and did not require any tools. Overall we are very satisfied with this table.
customer_reviews.author: R. Gundala

customer_reviews.title: Makes a nice presence in our entryway!
customer_reviews.text: This is a very nice piece of furniture for the price. The cabinet holds more than expected and there is plenty of room on the bottom shelf to add some holiday (or what ever day) decor!
customer_reviews.author: Granny41

customer_reviews.title: high quality, reasonable price!
customer_reviews.text: needed a table in the bedroom to put under the tv for a cable box. checked all the local furniture stores and wow. 400-500 for similar tables. received this one yesterday and put it together in 5 minutes. arrived in perfect condition. its looks even better in person. very well made and sturdy. the one i received was made in april of 2014, so stock is new. its finish and design matches our bedroom suit perfectly.
customer_reviews.author: Patrick A. Moore

customer_reviews.title: GREAT PURCHASE! FLEXIBLE PIECE!
customer_reviews.text: This is a beautiful piece of furniture and required very little assembly; took me about fifteen minutes to put it together. I originally bought it for my foyer to replace a chair I had had there, but after looking at it for two weeks, I decided that it was too small (depth wise) for my lobby. It now sits in my breakfast nook and looks beautiful in my newly remodeled kitchen area. The color is darker than it looks in this picture, so it easily fit into the black/light grey/gentle green Martha Stewart scheme of my new kitchen.
customer_reviews.author: Pooney

customer_reviews.title: Very nice piece and good price!
customer_reviews.text: We are using this as a entryway table. We needed a table not more than 42 inches in width and this was perfect. The storage is perfect for hats, small purses, umbrellas etc. It was very easy to assemble. Just needed to screw in legs and add the bottom shelf. Very happy with purchase.
customer_reviews.author: SBB

customer_reviews.title: beautiful cabinet
customer_reviews.text: i was really disappointed when i saw the table. the back left leg where it attaches to the base was chipped and scratched. the underside of the cabinet was smeared with stain like someone had cleaned their stain rag off on it.instead of sending such a heavy item back we filled the chips and scratches with putty then used a stain pen on it. it actually worked out well. the stain covered well enough that its not noticeable . the rest of the cabinet was nicely done and i love the design of it.
customer_reviews.author: pat abitz

customer_reviews.title: bad customer service
customer_reviews.text: recieved the package within a descent time frame, but came without some parts. Seemed to take forever and a day to get emails back and forth to have the part sent out. After 2 weeks of emails and waiting, the PART came, not parts. Amazing to say the least, buy here if you have nothing but time and lots of patience, I prefer a company that knows how to package a product or expedite a poorly packaged product, neither that I found here. Sending this back immediately for something else that comes all together.......
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Very nice piece of furniture
customer_reviews.text: I was leery of mail-ordering a piece of China-made furniture, but the quality of this piece is excellent. I could not find any flaws in the finish. Doors work as expected. Assembly took about five minutes after the box was unpacked. Place the table upside-down on a carpeted or padded surface, screw the four long leg segments into the threaded sockets, place the shelf on top of the legs, then screw the short leg segments into the long leg segments through holes in the shelf. Done.
customer_reviews.author: StraightShooter

customer_reviews.title: Called the manufacturer and they basically told me TS - called Amazon and their customer service was A++++++ 5 star - Love Amazon
customer_reviews.text: Cheaply made and glued together - glue started showing through the seams of the wood! Called the manufacturer and they basically told me TS - called Amazon and their customer service was A++++++ 5 star - Love Amazon
customer_reviews.author: Katherine M.

customer_reviews.title: This furniture is beautiful. The color and the design is just perfect
customer_reviews.text: This furniture is beautiful. The color and the design is just perfect. It only took 3 days for delivery and it came with no damage at all! Assembly is so easy! It will only take a minute to put the legs together. Beautiful just beautiful for a very low price! I wish they will make a bigger size, i would buy another one for my TV room! Love it!
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Lovely table
customer_reviews.text: This console table is a beautiful addition to my living room. It has a warm, sophisticated, and traditional look and the price is very reasonable. It appears to be a matter of luck whether your table will arrive damaged or not; I was lucky and it came in perfect shape. Assembly involves just screwing on the legs and takes only minutes. The table can be used with or without the bottom shelf; I like it both ways and may change the look from time to time. Shipping is expensive but it's worth it to get just the right piece. Recommended.
customer_reviews.author: Kona

customer_reviews.title: Doesn't look bad at all.
customer_reviews.text: I like the way it looks and it arrived in pretty good condition. I would buy again.
customer_reviews.author: Ferd Berfel

customer_reviews.title: Ok purchase
customer_reviews.text: For the price I pay it is a ok purchase. But I don't think it's worth the original price. I expected a high end wood piece from the picture, but the produce I received is more like a replica of the design. The right end corner was bruised and Little indented, not sure though shipping or just made like that. The two doors do not level, both has spaces up or down. The paint is not polished well as the picture shows, it's more a dull finish. If looked from distance, it serves the purpose in the foyer.
customer_reviews.author: meisusu

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful furniture
customer_reviews.text: Great packaging and very heavy. All edges and corners of the box had exterior reinforced/solid protection as well as interior thick Styrofoam protection around all edges and inside the cabinet itself. The reinforced protection was taped and banded on the exterior while the woodwork was wrappes and protected by Styrofoam. The quality of the cabinet is beautiful. Minor and inconsequential stain difference on the back edge, that will never be seen. The wood is solid. The construction is simple. All the parts are well made and good quality. Excellent piece I would recommend to anyone.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful nice color and finish
customer_reviews.text: Beautiful nice color and finish, easy to assemble. I purchased two and have one for each side of my queen bed. I placed a lamp on each and for one side of the bed a vase filled with flowers and the other side of the bed of course my Coffee maker with K cups. Under the table on the shelf I have folded fleece cozy blankets. I pamper myself and you should as well you deserve it.
customer_reviews.author: Tammy

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful and spacious table
customer_reviews.text: I adore this table. It is good quality, sturdy and even prettier in person. It fits in my entryway perfectly and the drawer is much more spacious than I anticipated. Great purchase, especially for the price!
customer_reviews.author: SMR

customer_reviews.title: Perfect accent piece!
customer_reviews.text: Spent a lot of time searching for a small accent table and finally took a chance on this one because of its size and visual appeal. Item arrived in perfect condition and very well packaged. Super quick and easy to assemble. Hugs the wall nicely and doesn't project too far into the room...which is the perfect profile for the space in which I'm using it. Falling just shy of 5 stars because I'm old school and I think my money should go a little farther. But, a good deal in comparison of others I've seen!
customer_reviews.author: Jen

customer_reviews.title: Great product
customer_reviews.text: When I got my entry table, it was packed so professionally I was delighted in their care of the product. Assembly was real easy, and it look great in the hallway. I am quite pleased with this item.
customer_reviews.author: Russell D. Bourne

customer_reviews.title: Nice piece of furniture and easy to put together
customer_reviews.text: Nice piece of furniture and easy to put together. Wish the top of the table had more of a woodgrain in the stain. Looks like it was stained just brown but the lower shelf has a more polished look which I would have preferred on top. Wouldn't call it high end furniture but looks good in my entryway.
customer_reviews.author: G.Walter

customer_reviews.title: absolutely beautiful!
customer_reviews.text: This table looks exactly as depicted. Very easy to put together. It was in it's place within 5 minutes of opening the box. Just twist on the legs and you are good to go. Looks expensive and my friends thought it was an antique! It looks great with a mirror above it in the open area of my hall (years ago an old fuel oil furnace apparently sat there). No imperfections on the one I received and would highly recommend this to anyone.
customer_reviews.author: Florida Ladybug

customer_reviews.title: A very nice looking piece of furniture and I liked it very ...
customer_reviews.text: I purchased this in August 2014. A very nice looking piece of furniture and I liked it very much until last week (March 2015) when I discovered the front, right leg had split up the center. The item has been sitting in the same location since it was purchased and has never been moved. Now I'm concerned for its stability and it doesn't look very nice with a large crack running up the leg. It's obviously either a defective piece of furniture or made of a very inferior wood if it cracks after less than 7 months. I really think Coaster Home Furnishings should replace this item for me if they are a reputable and honest company.
customer_reviews.author: Michael

customer_reviews.title: I'm in Love
customer_reviews.text: This is probably the most beautiful item I have ordered from Amazon. The look is elegant and sosphiscated. The material came scratch free and sturdy. It was soo easy to put together that it took me 30 mins. I placed it in the living room of my home and it gave the room such beauty that even my boyfriend was in awe of it. This is a product and company I am sure to order from again. I LOVE this console table.
customer_reviews.author: Ms. S

customer_reviews.title: Very fine pace !!
customer_reviews.text: What a beautiful pace of furniture very well made it looks so good in my dining room I was not able to find a flaw anywhere , China is really coming out with some very fine furniture at great prices it looks like it was made in the U.S.A. !!! Buy it you won't be sorry !
customer_reviews.author: lioness

customer_reviews.title: Looks good, interior roomy.
customer_reviews.text: I bought this over a year ago. I have it in my front foyer. It is well made and I like the finish. The only issue I have is that the top finish became spotty. I don't know if it was my cleaning people that did it, or if it was from the manufacturer. The doors are well made and the interior is really roomy.
customer_reviews.author: Debi

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful table
customer_reviews.text: It's a very pretty piece of furniture that was easy to put together. Only complaint was they didn't do a very thorough job of staining the parts where the pieces were glued together. Fortunately, we had a stain on hand and were able to fix it ourselves otherwise I would've returned it.
customer_reviews.author: Silly Librarian

customer_reviews.title: Received damaged item 3 times!
customer_reviews.text: I got to say I like this console! That's exactly what I want that's why I have been ordering it 3 times so far and received damaged item every time :( The return and getting the refund hasn't been too difficult but over all it's frustrating and disappointing. Not sure if I want to order it again!
customer_reviews.author: Rose

customer_reviews.title: Brown finish
customer_reviews.text: The console arrived in perfect condition. It is sturdy and it feels solid when opening and closing the doors. The color is indeed a rich dark brown. It is not as dark as walnut but is darker than a pecan finish. The piece I received does not have any red notes as described by some reviewers. Based on my computer monitor it is one shade darker than pictured and is a true brown. I would order this piece again. I ordered 4 items and with PRIME my shipping was 16 dollars and change.
customer_reviews.author: LMSKS

customer_reviews.title: Great Console Table
customer_reviews.text: Great table for the price! If you need a table with a small footprint don't hesitate to buy. Looks great in our foyer. Shipping was flawless, well packaged, and put together in minutes! Finish is more beautiful than I expected, have gotten many compliments.
customer_reviews.author: UF GRAD MOM

customer_reviews.title: Perfect for under a 36" wall-mounted tv.
customer_reviews.text: Arrived on time and in perfect condition. Doesn't stick out too far, but still adds valuable storage. This is well-made & heavy for it's petite look - higher quality than I imagined. I will refer back to this seller for future pieces. The round style allows it to easily slide into small areas. Storage area is far larger than I thought. I only wish it was 4 inches taller. LOVE this piece!
customer_reviews.author: Joolz

customer_reviews.title: It was a very dark finish which I like.
customer_reviews.text: Not thrilled it's a product made in China. However, I just put it together in about 10 minutes. It was packaged tight and secure. Nothing was scratched or broken. It was a very dark finish which I like.
customer_reviews.author: Gillian Swaby

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful!
customer_reviews.text: I could not be more pleased with this table! It looks exactly like the picture and is very sturdy.
customer_reviews.author: C. M. Wrenne

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful piece of furniture!
customer_reviews.text: Overall, I love it! I do recommend it. It fit just right for the space I wanted it to be in. True to it’s picture in Amazon.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful table but not reddish brown
customer_reviews.text: Beautiful table but not reddish brown, just dark brown. Was hoping it would be more of the color in the picture but it's a darker brown.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Very sturdy and solid
customer_reviews.text: I just received this table. It was really simple to put together! Very sturdy and solid. My only issue is it is much darker than in the picture. Other than that I am very pleased.
customer_reviews.author: Lynn Hansen

customer_reviews.title: However that was not the case with this table as it looks elegant and is quite sturdy. Best of all
customer_reviews.text: I bought this based on previous customer reviews, but was still somewhat hesitant as self-assembled furniture can sometimes look cheap and wobbly. However that was not the case with this table as it looks elegant and is quite sturdy. Best of all ... my wife LOVES it!
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Great table
customer_reviews.text: Love this little table. Looks great in my entryway hall. Super easy assembly (5 minutes max) just screw on legs. It does look darker then the picture.
customer_reviews.author: Jason R

customer_reviews.title: Easy to put together....but Smaller that expected.
customer_reviews.text: Well I needed a table to fill an empty wall, I should have measured out before I bought it. I like the table, has an old look to it, but it is of wood substance. It didn't take long to put together, 8 legs and base, no tools were needed ( except having to use some pliers to unscrew one of the bolts out a little bit because it was in to far to go through base then into the longer legg) I will just have to find something else to go on one side of it, since it was smaller than I thought it was going to be, but that was my fault for not looking at the length.
customer_reviews.author: Ronald Gragg

customer_reviews.title: Excellent value; well-made
customer_reviews.text: We looked for a long time to find a table with these dimensions. Furniture stores and consignment shops were far overpriced. We had never ordered furniture online, but took a chance and ordered this Coaster table. It arrived when promised, and was carefully packed. The only assembly needed was to attach the legs. It fits nicely in the space reserved for it. The quality is very good, and the careful construction will allow it to last.
customer_reviews.author: FL Oma

customer_reviews.title: You Won't Be Disappointed!
customer_reviews.text: Absolutely Stunning for the Price, a very rich looking piece of furniture. I am a single woman and was able to complete the minor assembly in about 5 minutes. It was more time consuming removing from the box, as they really packed this well! I am impressed with Coaster! Looks absolutely beautiful in my large hallway with a mirror above. Thanks Amazon for a very reasonably priced product!
customer_reviews.author: WasAllMine

customer_reviews.title: You get what you pay for
customer_reviews.text: Good price for what you see in the picture. the product on the other hand... not very well packaged. there were "chips" (not real wood so not really a chip) on the corners. i found the pieces in the box. the screws that hold the doors on came out when i opened the doors to check functionality. overall not very impressed. looks nice from far away though. amazon shipping was outstanding as normal though
customer_reviews.author: caleb Myers

customer_reviews.title: Great look
customer_reviews.text: This table was perfect for my foyer! At first i thought it was too small but now I see that it compliments the space it's in. Love the look of it!
customer_reviews.author: Aphrodite Teya Rios

customer_reviews.title: Too easy
customer_reviews.text: I read many reviews before deciding on this table. I have to say, they were very helpful. This table is very sturdy, extremely easy to set up and not hard to clean up afterwards. Just make sure you have your vacuum handy when you set it up. I left everything in the box that I did not have to remove. Put the table together. Turned on the vacuum and dusted the table off, inside and out, and put in place in 15 minutes. All styrofoam balls and scraps all gone and very little mess on my floors. Too easy! Table looks great in my entryway and hugs the wall nicely. Beautiful finish and functional.
customer_reviews.author: B I M Valencia

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful Console
customer_reviews.text: The console is beautiful and arrived in great shape thanks to great packaging and padding. The assembly was easy due to the cabinet arriving already put together. The assembly did not require any tools and only the upper legs and lower feet had to be attached. The console was a little smaller than I had anticipated, but the cabinet is a very solid piece of furniture and I plan to order a second console after the holidays.
customer_reviews.author: Wylandfan

customer_reviews.title: Coaster Storage Entry WayTable
customer_reviews.text: This table was an excellent buy. It is beautiful and suits our needs exactly. It was packaged excellently with supports on all corners for protection. One leg had a small blemish but was easy to cover. Will not hesitate to purchase Coaster products again, possibly in near future. Highly recommend; This table could be used nicely in a dining area or even living room and it is just as pictured.
customer_reviews.author: Kindle Customer Betty Cousins

customer_reviews.title: As beautiful in the picture
customer_reviews.text: As beautiful in the picture. Put this in my foyer in front of my door. It's a perfect fit. My husband thought it was way more expensive than what I bought it for. He couldn't believe the price when I told him. A great buy.
customer_reviews.author: Susan

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful table and Elegant look
customer_reviews.text: Very happy with this table really looking nice on my entire door, easy to assemble my husband took only 15 minuets to put it together and not cheap product that what I appreciate the seller worth every penny 👍
customer_reviews.author: daneta

customer_reviews.title: Great price, good quality!
customer_reviews.text: Great price, good quality! Cheapest price found for this product so far is Amazon..it's AMAZING! What you see is definitely what you get!
customer_reviews.author: Ndrea

customer_reviews.title: GORGEOUS
customer_reviews.text: I read all the reviews and after looking at everything else online!... I decided to give it a try since I trust Amazon and their return policy. Well, this table is FABULOUS and perfect for my living room right in front of my huge window. It is darker than shown but matched with other cherry furniture so worked out perfectly. It arrived well packed with zero issues....Love it!
customer_reviews.author: Rbnlyn

customer_reviews.title: The packaging was superb - it was wrapped up like Fort Knox - not a scratch nor a dent
customer_reviews.text: Very well made piece. It was simple to put together, and I am an older gal. At first I thought it might be a bit darker than the picture - but it blended right in with my other furniture, after I got used to the nuances in shade. I have had many compliments. The packaging was superb - it was wrapped up like Fort Knox - not a scratch nor a dent. I am very pleased.
customer_reviews.author: Auntie Bee

customer_reviews.title: Pretty good table
customer_reviews.text: This table is perfect for the space I wanted to fill. It doesn't stick out too far from the wall and overall it looks great. It has a little stain smudge on the front curve, but it isn't noticeable. One of the screws in the door hinge has stripped out and so the door catches a little when it is opened/closed. If not fixed, eventually this will leave a scratch on the shelf below the door. It was super quick to assemble, it came very quickly, and was delivered in good condition. For the price, it's a great piece of furniture.
customer_reviews.author: Sharpecookie

customer_reviews.title: Dark Stain
customer_reviews.text: Very nice looking, but much darker than shown. That's why I'm dinging it 1 star. It has a tendency to tip forward, but a safety strap is included. styrofoam packing, while very effective, is crumbly. I recommend unboxing it outdoors and bringing cleaned pieces inside.
customer_reviews.author: Robert Dane

customer_reviews.title: Demi line cabinet
customer_reviews.text: Very nice piece Just what I needed in that spot
customer_reviews.author: Verna G.

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful little cabinet
customer_reviews.text: VERY nice piece of furniture. Comes almost completely assembled; only needs legs and lower shelf attachment. No finish defects whatsoever. Nicely packaged... exactly what I wanted. Cabinet door hinges need a very slight adjustment, something I can easily do when I get a Round Toowit.
customer_reviews.author: Willie B.

customer_reviews.title: Bad Quality
customer_reviews.text: I purchased this item in July it has only been 4 months and the legs have began to split....it is a beautiful table and sits nicely in my dining room . I have had many compliments on this table however, I see the quality is not good if just after 4 months the legs begin to split........very disappointed.
customer_reviews.author: Candice Galgoci

customer_reviews.title: You'll like this table!!
customer_reviews.text: I love this table and I get so many compliments on it! The only issue that I had was that it was slightly unleveled but I adjusted the legs to balance it out and problem solved! Great color and good quality!
customer_reviews.author: ment03

customer_reviews.title: Expected more
customer_reviews.text: Not a bad piece but I expected more for what I paid. There was some cosmetic damage when we opened it. It was smaller than I expected, also. If I had it to do over, I would have definitely gone with something higher quality.
customer_reviews.author: AmandaKC

customer_reviews.title: This beautiful piece blends wonderfully with all of my dark furniture ...
customer_reviews.text: Absolutely gorgeous !! I was not expecting much-boy was I wrong. This beautiful piece blends wonderfully with all of my dark furniture in the formal living room. The color and detail as well as the style cannot be beat for this price. Assembly was easy as well.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: Perfect
customer_reviews.text: I wanted a smallish table with a little storage space for my main entryway. This filled the billed perfectly. It was easy to put together; looked exactly like the photograph and there was nothing flimsy about it. It did arrive with a very minor bit of scuffing on a side surface but it may just be an imperfection in the fabricated material. I was able to find a lovely mirror at the local HomeGoods that matched it perfectly, too. A GREAT buy. So glad I got it.
customer_reviews.author: Doone 22

customer_reviews.title: Elegant entry table.
customer_reviews.text: This far exceeded my expectations! One would never guess that I paid so little for it. Very easy to assemble.
customer_reviews.author: Minnie

customer_reviews.title: Very nice table. well packaged and came quickly
customer_reviews.text: Very nice table. well packaged and came quickly without any damage. It took less than 10 minutes to unbox, assemble (no tools required!), vacuum off and put in place. It has a quality weight to it and is not made of cheap pressboard.
customer_reviews.author: EveS

customer_reviews.title: As advertised.
customer_reviews.text: Put this together in 5 minutes. Doesn’t wobble. Looks great. Mine is a true medium brown. Perfect!
customer_reviews.author: Billy Duncan

customer_reviews.title: Fits my space perfectly.
customer_reviews.text: The table was packaged extremely well and getting the box open took longer than it took to assemble the legs and shelf. It arrived in perfect condition and was easy to put together. I have only one wish, though, that the table was a couple of inches taller. It looks great and the illusion of height will be created with the decor I put on it. I think this table was a good buy and I am very happy.
customer_reviews.author: CleanToday

customer_reviews.title: Just what we were looking for!
customer_reviews.text: Beautiful piece. Very well constructed. Took 5 minutes to put together (legs and bottom shelf needed attaching). NOTE - the bottom of the legs unscrew in order to put on the bottom shelf. Legs are inside the top piece. Fits perfectly in an entrance way or hall.
customer_reviews.author: Palacedove

customer_reviews.title: It looks nice from a far
customer_reviews.text: Poorly made cabinet. I returned it for a replacement but the other had damage too. It looks nice from a far, just don't come too close because you'll see imperfections. But for the money it's an ok buy.
customer_reviews.author: Milushka

customer_reviews.title: Looks great and fits the space perfectly
customer_reviews.text: Used this in a small space in our master bathroom to add some character and a little extra storage. It was easy to assemble. When it arrived there was some slight damage to a back corner but where we have it you cannot see it so we decided to keep it rather than deal with ordering a replacement. Also the staining is a little sloppy, but again not enough to return.
customer_reviews.author: Quick Base Junkie

customer_reviews.title: I love this piece of furniture
customer_reviews.text: I love this piece of furniture. It is a great table for my hallway. It looks just like the picture.
customer_reviews.author: Amazon Customer

customer_reviews.title: really happy with the purchase
customer_reviews.text: Very high-quality cabinet, really happy with the purchase. Everything is perfect and I was impressed on how easy it was to put together.
customer_reviews.author: Jay Tee

customer_reviews.title: The table was easy to assemble
customer_reviews.text: Arrived ed on time,however minor damage to the rear corner. The packaging seemed sufficient but I would speculate the damages occurred prior to adding the protective wrap to the original box. The table was easy to assemble. Quality not as good as I have hoped, but I purchased for my basement.
customer_reviews.author: T.D.G.

customer_reviews.title: Solid and handsome piece for your hallway!
customer_reviews.text: Arrived on time and couldn't be happier. It looks great and was easy to put together. The picture does not do justice to the amount of storage room behind the two doors provides. The magnetic catches on the doors are strong and the piece has the solid feel of being well built.
customer_reviews.author: Mike Meehan

customer_reviews.title: Looks great and was super simple to put together
customer_reviews.text: Looks great and was super simple to put together. Arrived quickly, but will have to touch up a corner, where it was slightly damaged. It had to put in the box already damaged, as the way it was packed extremely well. That is why only four stars as quality control should have caught it.
customer_reviews.author: Katie MacAuly

customer_reviews.title: classic
customer_reviews.text: This table is just classic. Easy to assemble and looks great in the living room.
customer_reviews.author: reza19

customer_reviews.title: Great addition to my house!
customer_reviews.text: Love this piece of furniture!! It was so easy to put together!!!! The lower legs were a little off but are separated by the bottom shelf. It had 2 small imperfections but I was able to cover up using a furniture marker. All the pieces were there. All in all, 20 minutes to put together. Love the compliments I get about this piece.
customer_reviews.author: Ruth Schleifer

customer_reviews.title: Damaged piece of furniture
customer_reviews.text: Item arrived heavily damaged. Box was dropped along the way, was delivered to house door and left. Once box was opened, the back panel of the product was completely broken off. The right back corners (top and bottom) were bent and broken, possibly broken when dropped. The front right door hinge is bent causing the door not to close correctly, damaged when possibly dropped. The box looked like an accordion on both ends where box was dropped. The box has multiple shipping labels, looks as if the box was returned, never inspected, and reshipped to next address. Had this item been inspected when returned last, the damages would have been seen. Beautiful furniture, but damaged.
customer_reviews.author: VT

customer_reviews.title: Great entry piece - had some shipping damage upon arrival
customer_reviews.text: I bought 2 of these and they are a good deal at a reasonable price. The quality I would rate a medium, not cheap but not a real solid wood with deep finish (you get what you pay for). Mine had some fair chips toward the back from shipping but I decided not to return since they were toward the back and the hassle to return seemed more than I was willing to do. They are perfect in my entry way and appear just as pictured.
customer_reviews.author: Susan L. Myers

product_meta.title: Entry Table with Curved Front and Inlay Shelf Brown
product_meta.description: Enjoy a rich provincial flavor in this stylish accent table. Built in a fetching half-round shape, its ornate sculpting and accent detail ratchet up the decadence factor. Rich brown offers a finish that's both warm and versatile. Traditional turned legs with an attached bottom shelf expand its utility and visual elegance. Make this accent table a fixture in an entryway or a main living space.
